snippet.title: Amber Heard secretly records Johnny Depp! Then LAUGHS?! Finally we see the FULL VIDEO!
snippet.description:
#johnnydepp #amberheard #justiceforjohnnydepp

Hey everyone! Welcome back!

I know some are wondering where I've been.  I followed the UK trial very closely, and am preparing some really big elements for upcoming videos.  I'll give everyone an update on the channel soon. Thank you for your patience!

In the meantime...here is the full video of Johnny Depp angry over his stolen millions, while Amber secretly records him.  The chopped up and edited version was leaked to TMZ almost 4 years ago, to the day.  Notice now at the end, Johnny does what Amber hates most and leaves, while she laughs at him.

See you all soon!

Nick Wallis Website (with documents and transcripts from trial):
https://www.nickwallis.com/depp-trial

My Twitter: @ThatBrianFella

My Instagram: @IncrediblyAverageBrian
